			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="P000594">Mr. Paulsen</sponsor> (for
			 himself, <cosponsor name-id="Q000023">Mr. Quigley</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="R000586">Mr. Renacci</cosponsor>, and
			 <cosponsor name-id="D000620">Mr. Delaney</cosponsor>) introduced the following
			 bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HJU00">Committee
			 on the Judiciary</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
